divs: Sighting DetailsDriving eastbound on buisness 80 at Marconi exit. daylight. Appeared to be a black kite with tail but seemed too high, tail moved but "kite" was motionless. High enough that if I saw a plane at same altitude would not of thought anything else.Stopped and watched for 15 minutes then I left.
